                           <desc>: Donation note.</desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez">
                              <locus target="#142vc">142vc</locus>: ዘመጽሐፍ፡ ዘማርያም፡ ሰበያ፡ ዘወሐባ፡ ሹም፡
